| # | Persona | Tier | Primary URL | Status |
|---|---------|------|-------------|--------|
| 1 | Hackers | Entry | observatory.unratified.org | Active |
| 2 | Teachers | Entry | unratified.org/educators | Active |
| 3 | Scientists | Entry | observatory.unratified.org/methodology | Active |
| 4 | Commercial Publishers | Delivery | (institutional) | License cleared, not yet engaged |
| 5 | Voters | Conversion | unratified.org/action | Active (content exists, persona now documented) |
| 6 | Politicians | Target | unratified.org/action/policy-brief | Active |

