     │                                 │                         │
  2  │ Land on specific analysis page  │ observatory.            │ Assessing:
     │ (often deep-linked, not home)   │ unratified.org          │ "Credible
     │                                 │ /methodology or         │ methodology?"
     │                                 │ /diagnosis              │
     │                                 │                         │
  3  │ Check methodology section       │ /methodology            │ Scrutinizing:
     │ Evaluate: framework soundness,  │                         │ "Does the
     │ epistemic confidence levels,    │                         │ discriminator
     │ transparency about limitations  │                         │ hold up?"
     │                                 │                         │
  4  │ Check citations — follow links  │ Sources throughout      │ Verifying:
     │ to original METR study, SF Fed, │                         │ "Primary sources
     │ Wharton PWBM, etc.             │                         │ check out?"
     │                                 │                         │
  5  │ Evaluate novel contribution:    │ /diagnosis,             │ Assessing:
     │ Does ICESCR-AI connection add   │ /higher-order           │ "Has anyone done
     │ something new to the literature?│                         │ this before?"
     │                                 │                         │
  6  │ Download citation (BibTeX/APA)  │ /data                   │ Incorporating
     │ Download underlying dataset     │                         │ into their own
     │ for replication/extension       │                         │ work
     │                                 │                         │
  7  │ (Some) Cite in their own work   │ Their publications      │ Extending the
     │ (Some) Propose collaboration    │ Email contact           │ analysis
     │ (Some) Critique in commentary   │ Their platforms         │ Engaging
