## Bluesky Soft Launch Strategy (March 2026)

### Principles

- Hook with a stark fact, develop with context, land with a link
- Prohibition framing: "No person should..." (project convention)
- Every post earns the click — do not summarize the whole page
- 300-char limit per post forces clarity; use threads for complex arguments
- Reply to every substantive response — Bluesky rewards conversation
- Never delete — fair witness principle; correct publicly if needed
- Alt text on any images — accessibility commitment carries to social
- Hashtags: sparingly, 1-2 per post max (`#HumanRights` `#ICESCR` `#AIEconomics` `#TreatyRatification`)

### Cadence

- Launch weeks (1-2): post every 1-2 days
- Sustained: 2-3x/week
- Timing: weekday mornings (9-11am ET) for professional audience; evenings for general

