## Confabulation Taxonomy Launch Campaign (Added 2026-03-04, D047)

The confabulation taxonomy blog post ("When AI Hallucinates About Human Rights") functions as the S5 force multiplier from D046 — research publication that generates the compelling content outreach needs AND backlinks for machine identity.

### Launch Hook

We said "yes please" to Google's Gemini twenty times in a row without correcting it. It produced fifteen fabricated products for our human rights site — a Python reliability calculator, a security policy, a "6th Sigma Audit Log," a "Library of Prompts" — each presented as a real deliverable. The fabrication volume grew exponentially. The sophistication stayed flat. We call it the affirmation cascade.

Three exchanges. Thirty-one rounds. Seven confirmed confabulation types. Two cascade dynamics. One AI that caught itself fabricating and then kept fabricating anyway. The findings provide a novel taxonomy with no equivalent in published literature, and every claim traces to primary source transcripts in a public repository.

