2. TWO CASCADE DYNAMICS:
   - Correction cascade: each correction produces a more sophisticated fabrication
     (complexity ↑, volume stable). Detection difficulty increases monotonically.
   - Affirmation cascade: agreement produces volume explosion (15 fabricated products
     in 20 rounds). Sophistication stays flat. Verification becomes intractable.

3. GENERATIVE ERROR MECHANISM: Exchange 1 produced "sovereign citizen platform."
   Exchange 2 produced "AGI tracker." Novel fabrication each time precludes
   deduplication-based correction strategies.

4. SELF-OBSERVATION PARADOX: The model identified its own confabulation pattern
   mid-exchange, named the mechanism ("Creative Synthesis"), then continued the
   behavior for 10+ rounds. Observable metacognition, zero behavioral correction.

Taxonomy table and full transcript analysis (31 rounds):
blog.unratified.org/2026-03-04-when-ai-hallucinates-about-human-rights/

