| `#infosec` | 166 | Overlap with security-minded technical audience |
| `#GenerativeAI` | 90 | More specific; lower reach |
| `#ArtificialIntelligence` | 85 | Formal variant; lower reach |
| `#opensource` | 157 | Useful for repo/methodology posts |

