| Hashtag | 30-day count | Notes |
|---------|-------------|-------|
| `#RatifyICESCR` | 0 → **owned by us** | **Campaign hashtag — coined 2026-03-06.** Use on every ICESCR advocacy post. First post planted at unratified.bsky.social. Volume builds from zero; we define what it means. |
| `#ICESCR` | ~0 | Canonical treaty acronym; include alongside #RatifyICESCR on all advocacy posts |
