| `#HRC61` | Feb 23 – Mar 31 2026 | UN Human Rights Council 61st session. ISHR (ishr.ch) actively promoting on Bluesky. **Use immediately — expires end of March.** Connect ICESCR non-ratification to current HRC deliberations. |

